        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-pixel-cyan/10 border border-pixel-cyan/30 rounded text-pixel-cyan text-sm font-semibold">
            Modern
          </span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-pixel-yellow/10 border border-pixel-yellow/30 rounded text-pixel-yellow text-sm font-semibold">
            Fast
          </span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-pixel-pink/10 border border-pixel-pink/30 rounded text-pixel-pink text-sm font-semibold">
            TypeScript
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <div class="hero-subtitle mb-12">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-pixel-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          A powerful Node.js framework built for developers who value
          <span class="text-pixel-cyan font-semibold"> speed</span>,
          <span class="text-pixel-yellow font-semibold"> simplicity</span>, and
          <span class="text-pixel-pink font-semibold"> elegance</span>
        </p>
      </div>

